modelVersions.name: Equitation
modelVersions.description:
This model its surelly not a masterpiece. It doesnt always work, sometime for some unknown reason you get a naked woman, sometime you get normal dresses. It might be that the word equitation creates a conflict with Chillout checkpoint for a few images it was trained on.

I also want to say, that in my posted images, i misstyped "wearing cap" it should be "wearing helmet" so correct it if you want an equitation helmet.

modelVersions.description:
Very simple to use, just use the keywords, maybe with 1.3 weight on them and 0.3-0.5 weight on the model.

The baseball glove keyword works most of the time but the glove is rarelly how you expect it, you need a lucky seed, and i advice to use it togheter with "throwing a ball" keyword, wich doesn't make the subject throw the ball how it was originally created but gives more chance to have a good glove.

I'm not really happy about this model because i couldn't teach him about racket, it usually draw wierd tennis rackets that might ruin the image. also placing holding tennis_racket in the negative prompt didn't work for me to not show these rackets, i hope you will get better results.

It works also with anime.

Enjoy!

Works also with anime.
